    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the activity of creating photographic images covering a very wide angle of view. In the digital realm, it has been applied to the construction of  virtual reality; as with panoramic exhibits of cultural heritage. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
